    "rank": 5,
    "text": "Like a vorpal dragon, you absorb life with an inhale and release it with an exhale. All living creatures in the first cone take 5d6 void damage with a basic Fortitude save. You and all living creatures in the second cone regain Hit Points equal to the greatest damage a single creature took from the first cone.",
